}

#playerSubtitleSettingsDialog QFrame#playerSubtitleSliderTile QLabel#SubtitleOptionSliderValue,
#playerSubtitleSettingsDialog QFrame#playerSubtitleSliderTile QLineEdit#SubtitleOptionSliderValue,
#playerSubtitleSettingsDialog QFrame#playerSubtitleSliderTile QLineEdit#SubtitleOptionSliderValue:hover,
